{
  "stem": "1061.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- this is a-- a-- a-- it's very, very strong impression left on me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember it to this day because the town was evacuated together with the surrounding villages.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we were caught in the cows and people and-- and-- and horses and peasants and the Jews, and everybody mixed in on the road into the forest.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And during the night-- of course, we thought, meanwhile, that Starachowice was just gonna be wiped off the earth.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And meanwhile we were sitting in these forests.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the German airplanes came down with the reflectors on their airplanes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were shooting people down in the forest, because, you know, there's a clearing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And people would go to sleep.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the cows would-- you would hear the cows.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you would hear the dogs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And whatever it is, whether they heard it in the airplanes or not, they came and they shot us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And finally-- of course, we were not hit during that night shooting when they would sort of pick us-- pick up the groups that they wanted to shoot at.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But eventually, as we moved on, we were caught in a valley between the Polish units on one side, on a sort of-- it wasn't a hill-- in a type of hilly area-- and the German units on the other.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were caught in the middle, in the crossfire.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this was just a horrendously frightening experience, because this was really my first war experience.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And mother insisted that we will wear our best clothes, the newest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I had a pair of shoes, brand new shows bought for the Jewish holidays.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I put on these shoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
